WEBVTT

00:00:02.023 --> 00:00:04.642
Sjajno je vratiti se.

00:00:04.666 --> 00:00:07.368
Volim ova divna okupljanja.

00:00:07.392 --> 00:00:09.589
Mora da se pitate: „Šta je sad ovo?

00:00:09.613 --> 00:00:11.265
Postavili su pogrešan slajd?”

00:00:11.289 --> 00:00:12.447
Ne, ne.

00:00:13.426 --> 00:00:17.638
Pogledajte u ovu veličanstvenu zver

00:00:17.662 --> 00:00:21.166
i postavite pitanje – ko ju je osmislio?

00:00:23.152 --> 00:00:27.062
Ovo je TED - tehnologija, zabava, dizajn -

00:00:27.086 --> 00:00:28.825
a evo krave muzare.

00:00:28.849 --> 00:00:32.210
To je prilično čudesno 
dizajnirana životinja